Name: Average time from Manuscript Export Succeeded to Plagiarism Originality Report Completed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed'

Name: Total time between Manuscript Export Succeeded and SW-Checklist Completed across variants that include both activities
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Average time for Manuscript Export Succeeded when it occurs before SW-Reviewer Agreed compared to when it occurs after a revision cycle
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Elapsed time between Manuscript Export Succeeded and SW-Reviewer Agreed in variants where SW-Reviewer Agreed eventually occurs
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Average waiting time to Manuscript Export Succeeded after Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation in first-submission cases versus resubmission cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Total resolution time of Manuscript Export Succeeded in variants that lead to RW-EIC Accept versus those that loop through multiple major revisions
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'RW-EIC Accept'

Name: Minimum time between Manuscript Export Succeeded and First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation in post-acceptance production phases
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation'

Name: Time of Manuscript Export Succeeded relative to the start of the case in variants containing SW-Reviewer Agreed, to assess its role as an early or late milestone
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and the end of case where activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed occurs

Name: Average time from Manuscript Export Succeeded to SW-AE Assign Reviewers in variants where reviewer assignment succeeds on the first attempt versus those requiring multiple attempts
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Elapsed time between Manuscript Export Succeeded and Manuscript Export Succeeded in multi-export variants, measuring re-export intervals linked to revision resubmissions
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Time until Manuscript Export Succeeded is performed after SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion in standard versus delayed checklist completion paths
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Average time it takes Manuscript Export Succeeded after the execution of Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission in cases where co-author creation precedes export
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission' and activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Minimum time it takes Manuscript Export Succeeded to be followed by SW-Awaiting AE Assignment in accepted versus rejected manuscript trajectories
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'
